data.description: Welcome to this charming Cape Cod that is nestled on over 1 acre of land that provides ample opportunity for outdoor enjoyment and recreation, from gardening to entertaining within the serene embrace of nature. Did I mention a 5-minute walk to the Wallkill River as well. Let's step onto the new walkway that leads to the side and front door. Inside you will find hardwood flooring, an updated kitchen with tiles and a bathroom that's been updated as well. All 3 bedrooms are nicely sized. The dining area has sliding doors that lead to a large, enclosed deck and an open deck as well. The basement offers ample storage space..
